Package com.googlecode.sarasvati.env

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AttributeConverter
    Interface for converting to and from objects and strings.
    Env
    Env extends ReadEnv to allow add/changed/removing attributes.
    ReadEnv
    A ReadEnv is a container for attributes that can be read but not changed.
    TokenSetMemberEnv
    Similar to Env, except that attributes can be tied to the specific member index of a token set member.
